{"tid":676320,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"UCLA Summer study abroad","createTime":"2018-05-24T09:24:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T14:37:28.000Z","uid":118234,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"87b304670768d5a099ed614e5905a40b4d5f5bed","tid":676320,"uid":118234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T09:24:32.000Z","msg":"係咁既... 小弟想去UCLA既summer session C (6 weeks program)exchange，但想讀既個2科同自己既major冇咩關係，但係credit bearing. <br />\n<br />\n因為我屋企好窮，好驚佢USA個visa唔批<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  學校個website話要證明自己户口有7900usd，加比400既non refundable registration fee就會幫我搞個I-20 form同簡科.  我個户口只係會show到8000usd左右(問mama借)，而港幣個邊只係會show到一萬左右，好驚佢唔批我visa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   唔批的話會曬 好多錢，包括sevis, registration加1280既appointment fee, 呢到加加埋埋都成6000hkd大元，好驚佢唔批啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而我屋企整係得mama搵錢，搵1萬頭一個月，其實個邊d學費同住宿費都係我自己出去做pt搵番尼，但上網睇話個簽證官會問邊個幫你比，邊個係你sponsor之類，我會答係我mama同學校(學校有20000hkd 資助)，我唔敢答係自己出啊，我驚佢以為我會過去打黑工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇人可以suggest下我點答好，同埋到底去唔去好，最驚就係佢唔批visa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <em></em>"},{"pid":"15fedee8da634fe8e139d9a6d6d28aabee6e4499","tid":676320,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T09:29:25.000Z","msg":"尼你老母<br />\nbtw student visa好少唔批, 你跟足通常冇死"},{"pid":"092eccfe0c20b8a97bcd77852dd23303b80281cf","tid":676320,"uid":69014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T09:35:41.000Z","msg":"其實你可以直接將你媽媽既戶口存摺遞比領使睇, 而唔需要將筆錢轉落自己戶口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過而家筆錢已經喺你戶口, 你都可以照直同領使講筆錢係你打工儲番黎, 應該唔太影響個申請結果, 因為佢批唔批主要係睇你喺香港有冇ties, 例如工作、家庭、學業, 而唔係睇你多唔多錢, 你證明到有ties就可以"},{"pid":"ca5cc051725036c108fade7051632d8d0fec69a1","tid":676320,"uid":118234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"092eccfe0c20b8a97bcd77852dd23303b80281cf","tid":676320,"uid":69014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T09:35:41.000Z","msg":"其實你可以直接將你媽媽既戶口存摺遞比領使睇, 而唔需要將筆錢轉落自己戶口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過而家筆錢已經喺你戶口, 你都可以照直同領使講筆錢係你打工儲番黎, 應該唔太影響個申請結果, 因為佢批唔批主要係睇你喺香港有冇ties, 例如工作、家庭、學業, 而唔係睇你多唔多錢, 你證明到有ties就可以"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T16:57:23.000Z","msg":"我上網睇左就係話如果係自己比既話佢會驚你去個到打黑工... 上網睇左好多例子都覺得美國好唔歡迎d窮人..."},{"pid":"b4b9dfa915d3b493ec75130411b57da1761494c2","tid":676320,"uid":187316,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T17:30:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f704eecff900c51204b9a6591b2d2bef654c496f","tid":676320,"uid":187316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T17:32:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"96eef0bb7140609d220232699b97dc1ab862b6d7","tid":676320,"uid":187316,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T17:34:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09f614aee7379a6d6f561b6c9fa131726ed8ff58","tid":676320,"uid":118234,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b4b9dfa915d3b493ec75130411b57da1761494c2","tid":676320,"uid":187316,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T17:30:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T04:35:25.000Z","msg":"我想簡讀天文學同心理學，我major其實係bba個邊，但我唔想讀番major既野，所以簡呢2科。天文同心理都係一d入門級數既野"},{"pid":"644a0e508d169e7e24b7c87fa40d5debfc706efc","tid":676320,"uid":77850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96eef0bb7140609d220232699b97dc1ab862b6d7","tid":676320,"uid":187316,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T17:34:30.000Z","msg":"此回